in holds a bachelor of arts degree in economics from knox college in galesburg illinois       follow us on                        contact us    privacy policy    terms of use    ca transparency in supply chain act    conflict minerals information our team pictures photos documents site pages lists discussions sites anderson newlin craig evans brooks bridges jacksonbridges people and groups